data.description: Welcome home to this gorgeous 2-story residence in Kyle, TX, nestled between Austin & San Antonio. Close to shopping and major highways, this home features a loft and a bedroom with a full bathroom upstairs. Enjoy the open floor plan with modern kitchen appliances and ample natural light. The main level includes a spacious primary suite with a great bathroom featuring a walk in shower. There are three bedrooms on the main floor with the fourth bedroom upstairs with a full bathroom and game room. Outside, the cozy backyard is perfect for relaxing or entertaining under your covered patio. Don't miss out – schedule your showing today!! Contact agent today for preferred lender buyer Incentives!
